findings.title: Minting of incorrect token level
findings.description: When ascending two tokens to create a token of a higher level, there is no check to ensure that the new token ID is within the range of token IDs for the desired token level.

findings.title: Logical Issues: Ascending Tokens to Incorrect Level
findings.description: When ascending two tokens to create a token of a higher level, there is no check to ensure that the new token ID is within the range of token IDs for the desired token level, resulting in mints of tokens in this new level to stop functioning.
